About:
Amber O'Neal is an American professional wrestler, better known by her ring names  Amber Holly and currently Amber Gallows.

She formerly wrestled in Ring of Honor (ROH) in their "Women of Honor" division as well as various promotions on the U.S. independent circuit. Gallows is a former NWA World Women's Champion. She has also appeared in New Japan Pro Wrestling (NJPW) as a valet for the villainous Bullet Club stable.
